### **Codebook for `reshaped_travel_data`**  

#### **Dataset Description**  
This dataset contains information on the number of travelers or residents categorized by year, district, nationality, gender, and count. It is structured in a tidy format, making it suitable for analysis in R using the Tidyverse framework.  

---
  
  ### **Variable Information**  
  
  | Variable Name | Class | Description | Example Values |
  |--------------|-------|-------------|---------------|
  | `year` | Integer | The year in which the data was recorded (ROC calendar). | `110` (2021), `112` (2023) |
  | `district` | Character | The administrative district in Taiwan. | `"鹽埕"`, `"鼓山"`, `"左營"` |
  | `nationality` | Character | The nationality of the individual. | `"印尼"`, `"馬來西亞"`, `"越南"` |
  | `gender` | Character | The gender of the individual. | `"男性"`, `"女性"` |
  | `count` | Integer | The number of individuals in this category. | `1`, `6`, `253` |
  
